  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "General Manager",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for an experienced <strong>General Manager</strong> to lead business operations, drive strategic growth, and oversee day‑to‑day management across the organization. The ideal candidate is a strong leader with solid business acumen and the ability to optimize performance, profitability, and customer satisfaction.</p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li>Lead overall business operations and ensure efficient daily workflow.</li><li>Develop and execute business strategies to support company growth.</li><li>Manage budgets, financial performance, and operational KPIs.</li><li>Build and mentor high‑performing teams across departments.</li><li>Strengthen client relationships and support business development initiatives.</li><li>Ensure compliance with policies, regulations, and governance standards.</li><li>Provide performance reports and recommendations to senior leadership.</li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li>Degree in Business, Management, or related field (MBA preferred).</li><li>8+ years of business management or operations experience, including leadership roles.</li><li>Strong financial, operational, and strategic planning skills.</li><li>Excellent communication, problem‑solving, and people‑management abilities.</li><li>Proven track record in driving business improvement and growth.</li></ul>",
